InfectedLine

Remote administration with command line through web panel.

Setup instructions:
1. Upload Web Panel to your hosting
2. Open Form1.cs and configure URLs in AppInfo class
3. Build Visual Studio Solution

Usage instructions:
1. Open InfectedLine.exe
2. Go to Web Panel and type commands to execute on remote machine
